{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "c9bad0e8-2bd7-4ced-be83-11229dd230bf",
    "name": "RENT_NEST Copy",
    "description": "RENT_NEST is a REST API for a rental property marketplace, supporting tenants, landlords, and admins.\n\n**Folders:**\n- AUTH: Registration, login, and session/profile retrieval.\n- PROPERTY: Public browsing of property listings and categories.\n- LANDLORD: Property management and rental request handling for landlords.\n- ADMIN: Platform-wide administration of rentals, properties, and users.\n- REVIEWS: Tenant reviews for properties.\n- RENTAL: Tenant-initiated rental requests.\n- PAYMENT: Stripe-based payments for approved rental requests.\n\n**Base URL:** All requests use the `{{base_url}}` collection variable (default `http://localhost:5000`). Update this variable to point at a different environment (staging, production, etc.) without editing individual requests.\n\n**Authentication:** Most endpoints outside of AUTH (register/login) and the public PROPERTY endpoints require a Bearer token obtained from the Login request, supplied via the `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header (see the PAYMENT folder for an example using the `{{tenantToken}}` variable).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "25588597",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/25588597-c9bad0e8-2bd7-4ced-be83-11229dd230bf?source=collection_link"
  },
