      "description": "Endpoints for user authentication and account access. Includes user registration, login, and retrieving the authenticated user's own profile.\n\n**Authentication:** Register and Login do not require authentication. 'Get Own Profile' requires a valid Bearer token obtained from Login.\n\n**Typical workflow:** Register -> Login -> use the returned access token as a Bearer token for subsequent authenticated requests -> Get Own Profile to verify the session."
    },
